query:
WITH new_room AS (
            INSERT INTO room (name, join_code, max_members)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
            RETURNING id
        )
        INSERT INTO room_member (room_id, name, fingerprint, public_key, is_owner, seed_commitment)
        SELECT
            new_room.id, $4, $5, $6, TRUE, $7
        FROM new_room
        RETURNING id
